        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_PRO/Scenes/Missions/CoastalTown/_scene_octopus.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 9ee7b5bc-2a0a-4303-bcaf-4fcce64022cb).Image",
        "Description": "Welcome to the coastal town of Sapienza. 47 your targets are a group of rogue chefs that are serving expired spaghetti sauce to their customers. Your client&apos;s have found out about this and have requested that you enter the kitchen and eliminate the threat. \r\rClient&apos;s wish is that each target are taken down with the cans of expired sauce they are serving. \r\rYour mission is active 47. I will leave you to prepare.",
